trum.\nHence, this method of computing indirect imprints of $f_{_{\\rm NL}}$ on angular\npower spectrum of CMB provides a new avenue to explore primordial scalar\nnon-Gaussianity and possibly constrain them effectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Apr 2023 16:05:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-17"}
