ted from magnetic helicity conservation. This also\nhappens when the initial total chirality is imbalanced. Our findings have\nimportant implications for baryogenesis after axion inflation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Apr 2023 15:26:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-14"}
